     SHORT="swfdec is a flash animation and game rendering library."
      LONG="
swfdec is a library for rendering Flash animations and games.
It was originally designed to be used for creating Flash 
plugins for GStreamer, but is a fully standalone library 
that only requires the libart library for drawing.
It includes a GTK+ player (swf_play) and a Mozilla plug-in.
